Blurrr 1.9.60 Update: Engine Overhaul for an Enhanced Video Creation Experience! Dear Creators We are thrilled to announce a significant update for Blurrr! This version marks a pivotal moment as we ve dedicated extensive time and effort to completely overhaul the underlying engine delivering an unparalleled creative experience for you. Upgrade Highlights: New Engine: Blurrr 1.9.60 introduces superior effects and professional grade rendering speeds. Text Shape Enhancements: Comprehensive upgrades to text and shape functionalities now supporting lossless scaling unaffected 3D toggling and newly added support for emoji inclusion. Effects Enhancement: Special effects motion blurs blend modes and more refined and professional enhancements. Material Resource Transfer: Deleting materials from the system album no longer impacts project use. We recommend timely clearing of album materials to save space. This update holds immense significance for us. We persistently strive to provide you with the most cutting edge video creation tool. Sincere thanks for your ongoing support and trust in Blurrr. This update is pivotal for us. We re continuously striving to equip you with top tier video creation tools. Thank you for your unwavering support and trust in Blurrr. Stay tuned for more exciting features to come including robust creative tools such as the Particle System and Text Animation. We are diligently working to present you with more creative possibilities. Update to version 1.9.60 now and embark on an entirely new video creation experience! We eagerly await your feedback and suggestions. Your input is invaluable to us. Feel free to contact us at any time: Follow us on: instagram:Search blurrrapp YouTube Search Blurrr DC https: discord.gg smXfWrbZ Infinite Creativity Advancing Together with Blurrr! Warm Regards Blurrr Product Team
